Title: Nature'S Gold Bleach(43 g)
Description: Your best friend?s wedding is around the corner and you have decided to go all out for her sake. Naturally, you will want to look your best and you have tried out every home-made remedy in the book, but to no avail. Brighten things up in a jiffy thanks to the Nature's Essence Gold Bleach that will give your skin a true royal experience while boosting its natural complexion. Your innocent skin takes on the relentless attack of the sun, dust, dirt and pollution all day long; it is bound to look lifeless and dull. Don?t tax your skin further - take the natural route to flawless, beautiful skin. Infused with a gentle yet effective herbal mid-formula that breathes a new life into your skin cells, this facial bleach is your ticket to healthy glowing facial skin that looks younger by years. Perfect for those last minute makeovers and grand beautification plans alike, every woman would do good to have this Gold Bleach on her dressing table.Inclusive of a rich herbal cream bleach and an activator powder to give your skin the tender loving care it needs, this bleach is incredibly gentle on your skin and makes for a hassle-free bleach application, minus the irritation and the tears. Go ahead, say hello to firm, supple facial skin that is resplendent with health.Directions for UseTake a liberal amount of the cream bleach on a mixing tray.Add to this, the suggested amount of activator powder.Using a spatula mix the contents till the crystals dissolve in the cream bleach.Taking care to avoid the sensitive eye area, apply it over your face and neck region.Leave it on for 5 - 20 minutes depending on your skin tone.Wash it away with water to reveal bright, radiant skin.Avoid soap for 5 hours after application of bleach.

Title: Burberry Brit - Set of 2 (2 x 100 ml) EDT  -  200 ml(For Women)
Description: A timeless fragrance for the woman who is bold and charming, this fresh and sensual Brit EDT from Burberry spreads a lush aroma that boasts of her individuality. Freshness at the Top The EDT opens with the fresh and soft floral notes of green almond, Italian lime and icy pear that complement her charismatic persona. Sweetness at its Heart At its heart, this EDT reveals the alluring aroma of white peony and sugared almonds that bring out the sweetness in her. Base Note The EDT finishes with a characteristic trail of amber, mahogany, vanilla and tonka bean, that intensifies and adds class to her character. Pack of 2 This is a combo pack that contains 2 bottles of 100 ml each, that can be bought for personal use or as a gift for a friend.

Title: Azzaro Chrome Legend - Set of 2 (2 x 125 ml) EDT  -  250 ml(For Men)
Description: Azzaro's Chrome Legend takes the sophistication of the couture conscious man a notch higher with its heavenly fresh and woody scent. A dab of this perfume will make him stand out in the crowd and spread the luscious aroma. Top Note This sensual and masculine fragrance has spices, apple, orange and aquatic notes in the top that complement his lively way of life. Heart Note The heart of this timeless fragrance is infused with the goodness of moss, sea-spray and musk that will leave him refreshed. Base Note Waves of harmony combined with cedar, tonka bean and vetiver form the base note of this perfume and will enliven his senses.

Title: Boss Grey - Set of 2 EDT (2 x 100 ml)(For Men)
Description: Hugo Boss brings the contemporary man this sensual elixir that gives rise to a heavenly ambience wherever he goes. Heart Note He can lose himself in the whiff of this refined and sophisticated fragrance that has a heart of jasmine, lavender, geranium and patchouli. Base Note An amalgam of musk, pine needle and sandalwood reveals the deep aroma of the base note.
